    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231170/extras/b88e7e810485c7eb728829deb4345f92.avif?t=1731860824\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231170/extras_big/b88e7e810485c7eb728829deb4345f92.avif?t=1731860824 width=800 height=250 /></span><strong>重力城堡</strong>（Gravity Castle）是一款利用重力探索神秘地下遗迹的2D闯关游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >位于世界中心的巨大的地下遗迹：重力城堡。虽然任何人都可以踏入重力城堡，但一旦关上门就无法再次逃脱。这座城堡，是谁，为什么，又是什么时候建成的，你在这片一切未知的的深渊之中，睁开了双眼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231170/extras/ae20528e3c74a12dc6098371b74acf8d.avif?t=1731860824\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231170/extras_big/ae20528e3c74a12dc6098371b74acf8d.avif?t=1731860824 width=800 height=250 /></span>为了生存，你必须要揭开重力城堡的最黑暗的秘密。现在轮到你挑战任何人都无法挑战成功的试炼。请将之前挑战者们的痕迹作为里程碑，一步一步探索重力城堡的最底层吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对重力城堡中无尽的恶意，你高高举起了你持有的武器——那就是能够逆转重力的反重力装置，以及可打开生命之路的灵魂石碑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231170/extras/a5530722f6f8036093ee280dc77cf5d8.avif?t=1731860824\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231170/extras_big/a5530722f6f8036093ee280dc77cf5d8.avif?t=1731860824 width=800 height=250 /></span>但是比起武器，更重要的是永不停歇的步伐。重力城堡永远不会宽容每一个轻言放弃的人。此时此刻，有某种东西正在下方的黑暗之中，等待着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是时候开始最后一次冒险了！</p>",
